  <main id="main">
    <div class="container">
      <section class="hero">
        <article class="hero-card hero-copy">
          <div class="eyebrow">24/7 roadside support</div>
          <h1>Get current location, live tracking, and emergency vehicle services in one place.</h1>
          <p class="lead">This page includes login with name, mobile number, OTP, and location, plus mechanic service, fuel request, towing support, and battery jump assistance.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://d2z0o16i8xm8ak.cloudfront.net/web/direct-files/06378392c58cdb47e5bce8f8bd09cdf0/90bda8e5-9d73-4f2c-93a6-44a9f15d5444/814a5b85.html?__&amp;Signature=rgswkBRNzBYgqItgaeCsJJ6YY1hjprkhWcwn~NPAHlL0gjVMfv80vNsSkVC6jHakfqmESIzhBKEmzvM-4LGIK31cU8cI3tBu3Brlybjd96NT5GuYuxm4-uLuTwDWmqWjGqTTskPrEDKIgf2du0M8Zi-rKg2pA2OIyeHlNEO0qSsOuiYmhmksJIO52GpGbS99ON0g16qhm5eHw86uG5qnRabY1MvFc7T7ZGw05fmW5KvX7kqN8myKy4IzvCO-dFj2MaWUwQWn3elOhBLhh5IVYvDsiKnhRPwueBj65EZPFn-wCRf5QFLi6jW85gJ6QJcurGZufWbBwerk7sZp0OhjbQ__&amp;Key-Pair-Id=K1BF7XGXAIMYNX&amp;rnd=1776486164508&amp;utm_source=perplexity#login">Open login page</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://d2z0o16i8xm8ak.cloudfront.net/web/direct-files/06378392c58cdb47e5bce8f8bd09cdf0/90bda8e5-9d73-4f2c-93a6-44a9f15d5444/814a5b85.html?__&amp;Signature=rgswkBRNzBYgqItgaeCsJJ6YY1hjprkhWcwn~NPAHlL0gjVMfv80vNsSkVC6jHakfqmESIzhBKEmzvM-4LGIK31cU8cI3tBu3Brlybjd96NT5GuYuxm4-uLuTwDWmqWjGqTTskPrEDKIgf2du0M8Zi-rKg2pA2OIyeHlNEO0qSsOuiYmhmksJIO52GpGbS99ON0g16qhm5eHw86uG5qnRabY1MvFc7T7ZGw05fmW5KvX7kqN8myKy4IzvCO-dFj2MaWUwQWn3elOhBLhh5IVYvDsiKnhRPwueBj65EZPFn-wCRf5QFLi6jW85gJ6QJcurGZufWbBwerk7sZp0OhjbQ__&amp;Key-Pair-Id=K1BF7XGXAIMYNX&amp;rnd=1776486164508&amp;utm_source=perplexity#forms">Request service</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        <aside class="hero-card hero-visual" aria-label="Service overview">
          <div class="map-mock">
            <div class="map-grid">
              <div class="mini">
                <span class="muted">Live status</span>
                <strong id="heroLiveStatus">Tracking off</strong>
              </div>
              <div class="mini">
                <span class="muted">Nearest service</span>
                <strong>Mechanic</strong>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mini">
              <span class="muted">Current coordinates</span>
              <strong id="heroCoords">Waiting for location</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="mini">
              <span class="muted">Emergency response</span>
              <strong>Fuel, tow, battery, mechanic</strong>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </section>

      <section id="location">
        <div class="section-head">
          <h2>Current and live location</h2>
          <p>Use browser GPS to detect present coordinates and start live location tracking.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="status-grid">
          <article class="status-card">
            <h3>Current Location</h3>
            <p class="muted">Latitude and longitude</p>
            <div class="status-value" id="coords">Not available yet</div>
          </article>
          <article class="status-card">
            <h3>Area</h3>
            <p class="muted">Detected location name</p>
            <div class="status-value" id="area">Waiting for update</div>
          </article>
          <article class="status-card">
            <h3>Live Location</h3>
            <p class="muted">Real-time tracking status</p>
            <div class="status-value" id="liveStatus">Tracking off</div>
          </article>
          <article class="status-card">
            <h3>Last Updated</h3>
            <p class="muted">Latest refresh time</p>
            <div class="status-value" id="updatedTime">--:--</div>
          </article>
        </div>
        <div class="panel" style="padding:1.25rem;margin-top:1rem;">
          <div class="inline-actions">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" id="getLocationBtn" type="button">Get current location</button>
            <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="toggleTrackingBtn" type="button">Start live tracking</button>
          </div>
          <div class="output" id="locationMessage">Location messages will appear here.</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="services">
        <div class="section-head">
          <h2>Emergency services</h2>
          <p>Select the service you need and fill the request form below.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="services-grid">
          <article class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">M</div>
            <h3>Mechanic service</h3>
            <p class="muted">Report what problem happened with your bike or car.</p>
            <span class="tag">Problem diagnosis</span>
          </article>
          <article class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">F</div>
            <h3>Fuel service</h3>
            <p class="muted">Login and request petrol or diesel delivery to your current location.</p>
            <span class="tag">Fuel refill</span>
          </article>
          <article class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">T</div>
            <h3>Towing service</h3>
            <p class="muted">Request towing further to a garage, home, or service station.</p>
            <span class="tag">Vehicle towing</span>
          </article>
          <article class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">B</div>
            <h3>Battery jump</h3>
            <p class="muted">Get jump-start or battery support if your vehicle will not start.</p>
            <span class="tag">Battery support</span>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="forms">
        <div class="section-head">
          <h2>Login and request pages</h2>
          <p>All service forms are placed below in one responsive page so you can publish it directly on GitHub Pages.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="forms-grid">
          <article class="form-card" id="login">
            <h3>User login page</h3>
            <p class="muted">Add name, mobile number, OTP, and current location.</p>
            <form id="userLoginForm">
              <div class="grid-2">
                <label>Name
                  <input type="text" id="userName" placeholder="Enter your full name" required="">
                </label>
                <label>Mobile number
                  <input type="tel" id="userMobile" placeholder="Enter mobile number" maxlength="10" required="">
                </label>
              </div>
              <div class="grid-2">
                <label>OTP
                  <input type="text" id="userOtp" placeholder="Enter OTP" required="">
                </label>
                <label>Current location
                  <input type="text" id="userLocation" placeholder="Use current location" required="">
                </label>
              </div>
              <div class="inline-actions">
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="button" id="sendOtpBtn">Send OTP</button>
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="button" id="useLocationBtn">Use current location</button>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Login now</button>
              </div>
            </form>
            <div class="output" id="loginMessage">Login status will appear here.</div>
          </article>

          <article class="form-card" id="fuel-login">
            <h3>Fuel page login</h3>
            <p class="muted">Customer details for emergency fuel delivery.</p>
            <form id="fuelForm">
              <div class="grid-2">
                <label>Name
                  <input type="text" id="fuelName" placeholder="Enter your name" required="">
                </label>
                <label>Mobile number
                  <input type="tel" id="fuelMobile" placeholder="Enter mobile number" maxlength="10" required="">
                </label>
              </div>
              <div class="grid-2">
                <label>OTP
                  <input type="text" id="fuelOtp" placeholder="Enter OTP" required="">
                </label>
                <label>Current location
                  <input type="text" id="fuelLocation" placeholder="Enter delivery location" required="">
                </label>
              </div>
              <div class="grid-2">
                <label>Fuel type
                  <select id="fuelType" required="">
                    <option value="">Select fuel</option>
                    <option>Petrol</option>
                    <option>Diesel</option>
                    <option>CNG</option>
                  </select>
                </label>
                <label>Quantity
                  <input type="text" id="fuelQty" placeholder="Example: 2 litres" required="">
                </label>
              </div>
              <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Request fuel</button>
            </form>
            <div class="output" id="fuelMessage">Fuel request status will appear here.</div>
          </article>

          <article class="form-card" id="mechanic">
            <h3>Mechanic service page</h3>
            <p class="muted">Tell us what is the problem with the vehicle.</p>
            <form id="mechanicForm">
              <div class="grid-2">
                <label>Vehicle type
                  <select id="vehicleType" required="">
                    <option value="">Select vehicle</option>
                    <option>Bike</option>
                    <option>Car</option>
                    <option>Scooter</option>
                    <option>Auto</option>
                  </select>
                </label>
                <label>Problem type
                  <select id="problemType" required="">
                    <option value="">Select issue</option>
                    <option>Engine problem</option>
                    <option>Puncture</option>
                    <option>Brake issue</option>
                    <option>Electrical issue</option>
                    <option>Not starting</option>
                  </select>
                </label>
              </div>
              <label>What is the problem?
                <textarea id="problemDetails" placeholder="Describe the issue clearly" required=""></textarea>
              </label>
              <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Request mechanic</button>
            </form>
            <div class="output" id="mechanicMessage">Mechanic request status will appear here.</div>
          </article>

          <article class="form-card" id="towing">
            <h3>Towing service page</h3>
            <p class="muted">Book towing service for further transport of your vehicle.</p>
            <form id="towingForm">
              <div class="grid-2">
                <label>Pickup location
                  <input type="text" id="towPickup" placeholder="Enter pickup location" required="">
                </label>
                <label>Drop location
                  <input type="text" id="towDrop" placeholder="Enter destination" required="">
                </label>
              </div>
              <div class="grid-2">
                <label>Vehicle type
                  <select id="towVehicle" required="">
                    <option value="">Select vehicle</option>
                    <option>Bike</option>
                    <option>Car</option>
                    <option>SUV</option>
                    <option>Truck</option>
                  </select>
                </label>
                <label>Towing reason
                  <input type="text" id="towReason" placeholder="Accident, breakdown, etc." required="">
                </label>
              </div>
              <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Book towing</button>
            </form>
            <div class="output" id="towingMessage">Towing request status will appear here.</div>
          </article>

          <article class="form-card full" id="battery">
            <h3>Battery jump services</h3>
            <p class="muted">Raise a battery jump or battery support request.</p>
            <form id="batteryForm">
              <div class="grid-2">
                <label>Vehicle type
                  <select id="batteryVehicle" required="">
                    <option value="">Select vehicle</option>
                    <option>Bike</option>
                    <option>Car</option>
                    <option>Scooter</option>
                  </select>
                </label>
                <label>Service needed
                  <select id="batteryService" required="">
                    <option value="">Select service</option>
                    <option>Jump start</option>
                    <option>Battery check</option>
                    <option>Battery replacement support</option>
                  </select>
                </label>
              </div>
              <label>Issue details
                <textarea id="batteryDetails" placeholder="Vehicle not starting, battery weak, lights dim, etc." required=""></textarea>
              </label>
              <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Request battery support</button>
            </form>
            <div class="output" id="batteryMessage">Battery support request status will appear here.</div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <button class="sos" id="sosBtn" type="button" aria-label="Emergency SOS">SOS</button>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>RescueRide demo page for roadside assistance with current location, live location, login, mechanic, fuel, towing, and battery jump services.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  


